1.0.0.name: wordpress/jstat
1.0.0.description: jStat is a statistical library written in JavaScript that allows you to perform advanced statistical operations without the need of a dedicated statistical language (i.e. MATLAB or R). This plugin installs jStat and required jQuery plugins to your installation.
